These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, skateboarding, swimming, surfing
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, mexican, british, thai
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, tea, 7up
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
 2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
 3. the person drinking tea is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the left of the thai##8
 5. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
 6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the australian is the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the person drinking tea is not the thai##6
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##5
10. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the right of the british##8
11. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##8
12. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person who's sport is swimming and the mexican##2
13. the person drinking tea and the british have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |     3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | swimming | skateboarding      | surfing | skiing |
| Job           | british | thai | mexican      | australian |
| Music-Genre   | tea        | almond-milk            | 7up    | mirinda |

