.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, hiking, cooking, traveling
4 different pets are kept: goat, frog, guinea-pig, turtle
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, pall-mall, siglo, swisher
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the old-henry-smoker##8
 2. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
 3. the pall-mall-smoker and the owner of the goat have the same parity positions##9
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
 5. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
 7. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
 9. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
10. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
11. the owner of the goat is not to the left of the swisher-smoker##8
12. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the old-henry-smoker##8
13. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
14. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage      | hiking | board-games   | cooking     | traveling     |
| Music-Genre   | frog    | goat   | turtle      | guinea-pig    |
| Sport         | swisher   | pall-mall | siglo | old-henry |

