.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, sports, martial-arts, superhero
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, milk, cola
4 different games are played: whist, scrabble, backgammon, poker
 1. the person watching time-travel movies is not to the left of the person drinking 7up##8
 2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 3. the person drinking milk is the person watching time-travel movies##1
 4. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the person drinking cola and the person playing scrabble##7
 5. the person watching superhero movies and the person drinking 7up have different parity positions##9
 6. the person playing backgammon is not to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##8
 7. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 8. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5
 9. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the person playing whist is between the person drinking 7up and the person playing poker##2
11. the person watching sports movies is not the person drinking 7up##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | superhero | martial-arts     | time-travel  | sports |
| Nationality   | sprite       | 7up    | milk | cola |
| Pet           | backgammon       | scrabble | whist     | poker  |

