.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, van, bike, roller
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, gospel, trance, country
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, dressmaker, nurse, manager
 1. the person driving the bike and the fan trance have the same parity positions##9
 2. the writer and the fan gospel have different parity positions##9
 3. the fan ambient is on the right of the fan gospel##1
 4. the fan gospel is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
 5. the nurse is on the left of the writer##1
 6. the manager is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
 7. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 8. the fan ambient is the writer##1
 9. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the fan country##5
10. the fan ambient is between the nurse and the fan trance##2
11. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | roller  | train        | bike  | van |
| Hobby      | gospel  | ambient    | trance | country |
| Sport      | nurse | writer | manager | dressmaker    |

