.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, aristoff, old-henry, cain
4 different games are played: poker, whist, billiard, bridge
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, epic, sports, documentary
 1. the person playing poker is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 3. the person watching epic movies is not the person playing poker##6
 4. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 5. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5
 6. the siglo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the old-henry-smoker##5
 7. the old-henry-smoker and the person watching epic movies have different parity positions##9
 8. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
 9. the person playing whist is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
10. the siglo-smoker is not to the right of the aristoff-smoker##8
11. the person playing poker is not the person watching epic movies##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |       4       |
| Nationality   | siglo | aristoff    | old-henry   | cain       |
| Pet           | whist    | billiard   | poker | bridge        |
| Sport         | documentary  | spy | sports     | epic |

 